mapping.kiegel:
contribution >> Contribution > agent*
or
contribution >> Contribution > agent >> Agent > rdfs:label

mapping.turtle:
bf:heldBy <value> .
# with literal value
bf:heldBy [ a bf:Agent ;
   rdfs:label "value" ] .
Notes:
(BMR) Previous mapping used heldBy >> Contribution > role
I'd like to confirm use of bf:heldBy, but as property definition gives expected value of Agent this seems like the way to go.
